{
  "stem": "2830.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then they used to ship all that wheat to-- I don't know, Germany, whatever, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then later, that everything was--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--confiscated, because of the-- it got so bad that my sister-- is the one she was married-- she lived at the outskirts of Lublin, called-- near Lublin-- Glusk.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like beautiful place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had meals, you see?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All that meal-- flour-- the best flour, I remember-- they had all those meals.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were confiscated also.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the-- when the Germans moved in, they took the family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The ones they were well off-- they picked on the first ones they were well off.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my brother-in-law's-- brother-in-law and my father-- and the-- they took him out.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they beat him up-- the Germans-- so bad that he spit up blood.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then-- then that-- he recovered a little.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took him back and forth, just because they had all those things that a Jew-- why should you have anything?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They beat them to death.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was my sister's brother-- my-- my brother-in-law's brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Brother-- and a whole bunch of other people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, they were related.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were in the mills, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a big-- it was called Cross's Mill, the best flour in-- in probably in Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then it became so bad that I couldn't do anything, that I wanted to, like play with kids, or go out, or what.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We belonged-- I belonged to the chalutzim as a child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't had any meetings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My-- my parents wouldn't move, because it was too late.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then, even if you wanna get-- we didn't had anybody in the United States to have a sponsor--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to go to or what.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
